data.description: This exceptional 5-bed, 3-bath estate home is a true gem of luxury living. With a captivating split floor plan, updated white shaker kitchen, new flat tile roof, accordion hurricane shutters, and volume ceilings, it exudes both elegance and functionality. Enjoy the best of what Florida's outdoor living has to offer on your oversized, covered patio, with retractable awning and tranquil screened-in pool. Wake up to panoramic golf course views, all within the highly coveted community of Binks Estates. Zoned for some of the best schools in Palm Beach County and mere minutes from the renowned equestrian show grounds, this property defines premium living. Don't miss the chance to present this extraordinary residence to discerning buyers seeking the epitome of comfort and style!
